{"id": "1425159750743490622", "channel_id": "1424823326647517234", "type": 0, "author_id": "225960315467202560", "author_name": "ellezard", "author_bot": false, "content": "As a fellow new player, I absolutely recommend Salvador. He's a very low investment and easy char who can wreck faces and you already have him E2 which makes him an absolute unit as a dps. His S2 hit super hard and give enough shield to easily  pass all the \"Shield X% Amount\" achievement easily. He was trivializing the entire Chapter 7 for me.\n\nThrow Thai in to dupe his S2 (better with E2 to make them free) but if you can't fill the ult fast enough for it, you can always go with Hameln + Ryker and build toward rotating the entire deck with all the pick-up.  Double cast let you choose to fill up the blood furnace before you choose to go with a  shield or a nuke and a crit from that thing is not different from an AoE Exalt.\n\nIf not, just pair him with Blue for guaranteed single-target damage and more Con stat as more max hp will boost your bloodfurnace which result in more healing/shield/damage.", "timestamp": "2025-10-07T16:36:02.765000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1424823326647517234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
